WEBVTT

00:02.625 --> 00:03.921
Okay! Let's go.

00:03.922 --> 00:06.473
This was my dream having the restaurant.

00:06.474 --> 00:09.360
And the whole thing was
turning into a nightmare.

00:09.361 --> 00:11.161
Ah!

00:11.558 --> 00:14.239
Something was released here.

00:14.240 --> 00:16.192
It was nasty, it was dark.

00:16.193 --> 00:18.698
[Speaking foreign language]

00:18.699 --> 00:21.177
Something was coming.

00:21.178 --> 00:24.538
[Speaking foreign language]

00:25.171 --> 00:27.255
My heart was hammering in my chest.

00:27.256 --> 00:28.248
[Boom]

00:28.249 --> 00:29.906
Boom! Boom! Boom!

00:29.907 --> 00:31.109
I don't want to be here.

00:31.110 --> 00:33.830
It felt like that I wasn't alone.

00:33.831 --> 00:34.883
Ah!

00:34.884 --> 00:37.157
You just don't know what's coming next.

00:37.158 --> 00:38.958
Ah!

00:39.467 --> 00:41.468
Ah! Help me!

00:41.469 --> 00:44.229
- Ah!
- Help me!

00:50.800 --> 00:53.860
Dining with the dead.

00:54.799 --> 00:57.379
[Bells ringing]

